data.description: Must see!  Must see!  You don't want to miss this beautiful home in York Suburban Schools!  Offering over 3,500 square feet of finished living space, this home has 4 bedrooms, 4 full bathrooms, and a 2 story family room, to start.  The kitchen features quartz counter tops, breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, an abundance of cabinet space while also offering an area perfect for your  larger dining table.  All 4 bedrooms are fully carpeted and have walk-in closets.  The master bedroom suite has a full bath with jetted tub, separate shower,  and crank open skylights.  Spring is coming!  This home has an outdoor oasis that the whole family will love!  Inground pool, outdoor kitchen with stone pizza oven, audio hookups, lighting, and fenced in back yard!  This one will not last!
